title: Elevate Your Start: LiveStrong's 10 Min Beginner Treadmill Run - Follow Along and Thrive!
description:
Quick and flexible today! Lots of hills, but you can choose if you want to take this workout at a walk, a run, or a combination!

Check out where we got the workout from here: https://www.livestrong.com/article/13776955-10-minute-treadmill-workout/

11:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!
